gement in jails, sentencing, case management in prisons, informing discretionary release/parole, case management during parole, and determining probation. However, they can theoretically be used at any point during an individual’s interaction with the criminal legal system.\r\n\r\n<strong>For more on the basics of risk assessment tools, see:</strong>'),(69,36,'_more_info_for_pop-up_1','field_62b5709e7557c'),(70,36,'title_for_pop-up_2',''),(71,36,'_title_for_pop-up_2','field_62b570281175c'),(72,36,'description_for_pop-up_2',''),(73,36,'_description_for_pop-up_2','field_62b5706211761'),(74,36,'subtitle_2',''),(75,36,'_subtitle_2','field_62b57eb4e3371'),(76,36,'more_info_for_pop-up_2',''),(77,36,'_more_info_for_pop-up_2','field_62b570b77557d'),(78,36,'title_for_pop-up_3',''),(79,36,'_title_for_pop-up_3','field_62b5702b1175d'),(80,36,'description_for_pop-up_3',''),(81,36,'_description_for_pop-up_3','field_62b5706511762'),(82,36,'subtitle_3',''),(83,36,'_subtitle_3','field_62b57eb6e3372'),(84,36,'more_info_for_pop-up_3',''),(85,36,'_more_info_for_pop-up_3','field_62b570c37557e'),(86,36,'lilst_items_item_1',' “Public Safety Risk Assessment Clearinghouse,” Bureau of Justice Assistance, US Department of Justice, https://psrac.bja.ojp.gov/ '),(87,36,'_lilst_items_item_1','field_62b570ea75580'),(88,36,'lilst_items_item_2','“Use of Valid Actuarial Assessments of Risks and Needs,” National Parole Resource Center, https://nationalparoleresourcecenter.org/action-guide-use-of-valid-actuarial-assessments-of-risks-and-needs/selecting-and-validating-an-assessment-instrument.htm '),(89,36,'_lilst_items_item_2','field_62b570f575581'),(90,36,'lilst_items_item_3','Alex Chohlas-Wood, “Understanding risk assessment instruments in criminal justice,” https://www.brookings.edu/research/understanding-risk-assessment-instruments-in-criminal-justice/'),(91,36,'_lilst_items_item_3','field_62b570f675582'),(92,36,'lilst_items_item_4',''),(93,36,'_lilst_items_item_4','field_62b570f775583'),(94,36,'l