nt during an individual’s interaction with the criminal legal system.\r\n\r\n<strong>For more on the basics of risk assessment tools, see:</strong>'),(2584,229,'_more_info_for_pop-up_1','field_62b5709e7557c'),(2585,229,'title_for_pop-up_2',''),(2586,229,'_title_for_pop-up_2','field_62b570281175c'),(2587,229,'description_for_pop-up_2',''),(2588,229,'_description_for_pop-up_2','field_62b5706211761'),(2589,229,'subtitle_2',''),(2590,229,'_subtitle_2','field_62b57eb4e3371'),(2591,229,'more_info_for_pop-up_2',''),(2592,229,'_more_info_for_pop-up_2','field_62b570b77557d'),(2593,229,'title_for_pop-up_3',''),(2594,229,'_title_for_pop-up_3','field_62b5702b1175d'),(2595,229,'description_for_pop-up_3',''),(2596,229,'_description_for_pop-up_3','field_62b5706511762'),(2597,229,'subtitle_3',''),(2598,229,'_subtitle_3','field_62b57eb6e3372'),(2599,229,'more_info_for_pop-up_3',''),(2600,229,'_more_info_for_pop-up_3','field_62b570c37557e'),(2601,229,'lilst_items_item_1',' “Public Safety Risk Assessment Clearinghouse,” Bureau of Justice Assistance, US Department of Justice, https://psrac.bja.ojp.gov/ '),(2602,229,'_lilst_items_item_1','field_62b570ea75580'),(2603,229,'lilst_items_item_2','“Use of Valid Actuarial Assessments of Risks and Needs,” National Parole Resource Center, https://nationalparoleresourcecenter.org/action-guide-use-of-valid-actuarial-assessments-of-risks-and-needs/selecting-and-validating-an-assessment-instrument.htm '),(2604,229,'_lilst_items_item_2','field_62b570f575581'),(2605,229,'lilst_items_item_3','Alex Chohlas-Wood, “Understanding risk assessment instruments in criminal justice,” https://www.brookings.edu/research/understanding-risk-assessment-instruments-in-criminal-justice/'),(2606,229,'_lilst_items_item_3','field_62b570f675582'),(2607,229,'lilst_items_item_4',''),(2608,229,'_lilst_items_item_4','field_62b570f775583'),(2609,229,'lilst_items',''),(2610,229,'_lilst_items','field_62b570c97557f'),(2611,229,'lilst_items_item_5',''),(2612,229,'_lilst_items_item